import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { VideoService } from 'src/app/services/video.service'; import { Video } from 'src/app/shared/models/Videos'; @Component({ selector: 'app-video-page', templateUrl: './video-page.component.html', styleUrls: ['./video-page.component.css'] }) export class VideoPageComponent implements OnInit{ videos!: Video[]; constructor(private videoService:VideoService){ } ngOnInit(){ this.videoService.findAll().subscribe(data =>{ this.videos=data; }); } }
